description: Xtierra Inc., a natural resource company, engages in the exploration and development of precious and base metal deposits in Mexico. It primarily explores for zinc, silver, lead, copper, gold, and mercury deposits. The company holds 100% interest in the Bilbao project located to the northwest of Mexico City in the southeastern part of the State of Zacatecas; and the Laguna silver-gold-mercury project. Xtierra Inc. is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Timothy David Gallagher B.Com., M.B.A.
